# The rendered estate carries render-time-injected secrets (Spaces keys, EMBED
# token, the mesh_app BOARD_DATABASE_URL) baked into the mcp launch template.
# It is REPRODUCIBLE from the committed catalog + Secrets Manager, so it is never
# committed. Re-render with `go run ./cutover/render.go` (see README.md).
